fields.body:
Dear ADAPT,

Someone has flagged {{ the_item }}:

    {{ url }}

You can hide it or un-flag it here:

    {{ admin_url }}

The flagger's email address is: {{ email }}

Have a good day!

{% load currency_filters %}Hello,

We are pleased to confirm your order {{ order.number }} has been shipped.

Your order contains:

{% for line in lines %}* {{ line.title }} - quantity: {{ line.quantity }} - price: {{ line.line_price_incl_tax|currency }}
{% endfor %}

Basket total: {{ order.basket_total_incl_tax|currency }}
Shipping: {{ order.shipping_incl_tax|currency }}
Order Total: {{ order.total_incl_tax|currency }}

Shipping address:

{% for field in order.shipping_address.active_address_fields %}  {{ field }}
{% endfor %}

The AshTag team.
